{"type":"article_comment","id":113693,"parentType":"article","parentId":8432,"uid":12573,"contents":"林夕早已经因为支持占中而被列入“港独艺人”了，不过他的工作主要是作词而非演唱，封杀难度很大，只能绕过经典作品，偷偷抽走几个题材比较恶政隐的。<br>\n<br>\n说起来达明一派纪念六四30周年的歌曲也是林夕作词，大反贼坐实了，无需冲塔。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/vfwQtru.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vfwQtru.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/vfwQtru.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-11-17","agreeCount":13,"discussionCount":0}